  <brief_title>Prevention of Neutropenia After Using G-CSF With TAC Chemotherapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Optimal Timing and Duration of Daily G-CSF With Adjuvant TAC Chemotherapy in Node-positive Breast Cancer;Multicenter, Randomized, Open Label, Clinically IV Phase</official_title>
